snippet.title: KANYE WEST VERSES (Word Clouds!)
snippet.description:
I challenge you to make a haiku using only lyrics from one of these word clouds :)

I make all of my charts from scratch with open data sets. Here's where I got the kanye west verses and lyrics from: https://www.kaggle.com/somesnm/partyn...
Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k9m1Che05-s

SMASH that like button and subscribe if you like my videos! I try to get creative with the data that I find and try to tell a story with it. 

If you're new to my channel, I do data storytelling :) Hope you enjoyed!
